    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Scroll of Mage Armor</strong> (Level 1 Abjuration)</p><p>You touch a willing creature who isn't wearing armor, and a protective magical force surrounds it until the spell ends. The target's base AC becomes 13 + its Dexterity modifier. The spell ends if the target dons armor or if you dismiss the spell as an action.</p><p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S, M (A piece of cured leather.)</p><p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 action | <strong>Range:</strong> Touch | <strong>Duration:</strong> 8 hours</p><p><em>Classes: Sorcerer, Wizard</em></p>",
